title: lonestar state of mind
description:
Lonestar State of Mind


Genre - Comedy 


Starring:


Joshua Jackson - Earl Crest

Jaime King - Baby

DJ Qualls - Junior

Ryan Hurst - Tinker

Matthew Davis - Jimbo



Plot:


Earl is engaged to his step-sister Baby. Baby has entrusted him to take care of her misfit cousin Junior. Baby is also intent on leaving Texas for LA on Tuesday. When Junior and his recently released ex-con friend Tinker rob a pizza delivery boy and end up with $20,000 of drug money Earl is forced onto the scene, giving up his and Baby\&#039;s LA money to save Juniors limbs.



enjoy
